'desc': [u'

Bella Baby Refreshing Wet Wipes (10 Pieces) Price: Rs.54

Using a gentle wet wipe that is enriched with skin nourishing elements is always better than washing your baby after every nappy change. The Bella Baby Refreshing Wet Wipes are are enriched with Allantoin and Vitamin E lotion that will help in keeping your infant's skin nourished. Vitamin E is known to be a great skin hydrant that will moisturize the skin. After you use the Refreshing Wet Wipes from Bella Baby your skin wont lose moisture as the protective layer left behind by the wipe will prevent water loss. An effective cleansing property of these Bella Wet Wipes make them ideal to be used to cleanse your bundle of joy's skin during diaper change.

These wipes from Bella Baby are formulated in such a way that they have a pH of 5.5 that is neutral to the skin and this aids in preserving an ideal moisture level on the skin. With a multiple-use clip on the packet of this Refreshing Wet Wipes from Bella Baby you can conveniently seal and store the wet wipes. Apart from using it to wipe your infant clean you can also use it to keep your hands and face clean and sanitised especially while travelling.

Bella Baby Happy Aloe Vera Sensitive Wet Wipes (64 Pieces) Price: Rs.149

After changing your tiny tot's diaper you wash her to keep her clean and to sanitise her skin. This process can deprive her skin of the essential natural oils from her skin and make her skin susceptible to irritations and rashes. To avoid this you can use wet wipes that are enriched with skin nourishing components. The Bella Baby Wet Wipes have been created with these aspects in consideration. The Bella Baby Happy Sensitive Wet Wipes belong to the sensitive line of wet wipes that are ideal for an infant's delicate skin. These hypoallergenic wet wipes are enriched with Aloe vera extracts that have the power to heal and condition the skin. A delicate lotion of Allantoin and Vitamin E makes this Bella Baby Wet Wipes an effective system that moisturizes and cleanses at the same time.

The Sensitive Wet Wipe from Bella Baby has effective cleansing powers that make them perfect to clean your baby's skin after every nappy change. These wipes also leave a protective layer on the skin that will prevent any moisture loss from the skin. Further
